00049 void CHPQuantificationDetectionFileReaderTest::testRead()
00050 {
00051         CHPQuantificationDetectionData data;
00052         CHPQuantificationDetectionFileReader reader;
00053         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(reader.SetFilename("../data/CHP_quantification_detection_file"));
00054         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_NO_THROW(reader.Read(data));
00055 
00056         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.GetFilename() == "../data/CHP_quantification_detection_file");
00057         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.GetAlgName() == L"sig");
00058         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.GetAlgVersion() == L"1.0");
00059         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.GetArrayType() == L"test3");
00060         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(data.GetEntryCount() == 2);
00061         
00062         ParameterNameValueTypeList params = data.GetAlgParams();
00063         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(params.size() == 1);
00064         ParameterNameValueTypeList::iterator it=params.begin();
00065         ParameterNameValueType param = *it;
00066         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"an1");
00067         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"av1");
00068 
00069         params = data.GetSummaryParams();
00070         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(params.size() == 1);
00071         it=params.begin();
00072         param = *it;
00073         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"sn1");
00074         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"sv1");
00075 
00076         ProbeSetQuantificationDetectionData e;
00077         data.GetQuantificationDetectionEntry(0, e);
00078         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "abc");
00079         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.quantification == 10.0f);
00080         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.pvalue == 0.1f);
00081         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.id == -1);
00082         data.GetQuantificationDetectionEntry(1, e);
00083         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "xyz");
00084         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.quantification == 20.0f);
00085         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.pvalue == 0.2f);
00086         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.id == -1);
00087 }
